        "4": "Rapport d'engagement 2025\nem-lyon.com — section Société à Mission\nhttps://res.cloudinary.com/emlyon/image/upload/v1768830781/Documents-a-heberger/rapport-d-engagement-2025-emlyon-v4.pdf",
